<h2 style="margin:0 0 16px;color:#0A0F1E">Qarz eslatmasi</h2>
<p>Hurmatli <strong>{{debtorName}}</strong>,</p>
<p>Sizning {{companyName}} oldidagi qarzingiz haqida eslatamiz:</p>
<table style="width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin:20px 0">
  <tr style="background:#fef2f2"><td style="padding:10px"><strong>Qarz summasi</strong></td><td style="padding:10px;font-size:18px;color:#dc2626"><strong>{{amount}} soʻm</strong></td></tr>
  <tr><td style="padding:10px"><strong>Muddati oʻtgan</strong></td><td style="padding:10px">{{overdueDays}} kun</td></tr>
  {{#if dueDate}}<tr style="background:#f3f4f6"><td style="padding:10px"><strong>Toʻlov sanasi</strong></td><td style="padding:10px">{{dueDate}}</td></tr>{{/if}}
</table>
<p>Iltimos, qarzni imkon qadar tezroq yoping. Savollar boʻlsa, biz bilan bogʻlaning.</p>
